tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VideoFrameData (
    frame_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    frame_data BYTES,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    video_id INT,
    action_label VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE video_actions (
    video_id INT,
    action_id INT,
    start_frame INT,
    end_frame INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (video_id) REFERENCES video_frame_data(video_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (action_id) REFERENCES action_labels(label_id)
);

CREATE TABLE model_training_data (
    training_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(50),
    features BYTEA,
    label_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (label_id) REFERENCES action_labels(label_id)
);
